originalText.text: I lived on the fence FOREVER until I finally got real with myself and  realized I was just so tired of feeling unfocused about what I really wanted my career path to look like . This experience in the 2% collective is everything I needed. I needed a complete overhaul and clarity about what is working and not working with every aspect of my choices as a mature actor. Jen , Natalie, Amanda, Carol, Noam, Marco and Anneta have been beyond priceless  helping me get to the bottom of what changes I needed to make to up level my career and simply stop throwing darts at the wall once and for all. The sense of community in this group can't be overstated. It is palpable the change in energy that is effected in this process. I am just so grateful and have experienced a shift in myself that is liberating .. finally . I don't even think about the investment anymore., to me it has been worth every penny simply because of the confidence and support that I have already garnered  . zero regrets. so so grateful.

originalText.text: The best decision I ever made was joining Jen Rudolph's 6 month 2% collective. Jen and her team did an overhaul on my marketing materials including headshots, resume, reel and website. As soon as I completed the program, I had a zoom meeting with my voice over manager. He was blown away with my new marketing materials and my new shark mindset (Jen taught me this of course ) that he started submitting me right away. After applying what I learned from Jen, I  booked 3 Co-Stars within 1 year.  This is just the beginning. Hiring Jen Rudolph as my coach was the best investment ever!!

originalText.text: In the first month of the 6 month 2% program, I was contacted by a rep for Lionsgate studio to audition for a project they were doing. A couple of weeks later I booked a co-star role in an indie feature, which picked up a distribution company and played at the 2022 Cannes Film Festival. Into the 60th day of the 6 month program, a management team requested to represent me and we’ve been together ever since. I booked commercials and a role for tv. Jen’s laser focus vision placed me with a photographer that can capture my entry points to exact specificity. As result I have gotten auditions and with the same photos I was requested to sign with a modeling agency for their big and brawn mature division. Jen Rudolph’s 2% program speaks for itself with real results! I highly recommend it. Thank you Jen you changed my life!

originalText.text: Having just completed the 6 month program, I can attest to this program being life changing. Not just as an actor, which is where it’s all at - but as a human. Jen is an expert in her field & she has surrounded herself with a staff of kind, generous humans who are all experts in their fields. Jen herself is kind, generous & honest in her approach to help actors navigate a successful career to become one of the 2% of actors who book work! It’s a lot of work & the program is structured to ensure your success. Jen and her staff manage to make it fun! And I’ve met a lot of wonderful actors who are now friends ⭐️

originalText.text: Jen is a fantastic, fantastic coach, mentor and human being. She is wise, compassionate, down to earth AF, and wants you to succeed and achieve your dreams. She is there for you no matter what, and helps you on your progress as an artist, businessperson and person in SO MANY WAYS. Jen is knowledgeable on everything in the business, is savvy, on the beat, and knows what's up and is so generous in sharing her vast knowledge. She has a sixth sense when it comes to understanding artists, their energy, their way, and I am so grateful that our paths crossed in this lifetime. I appreciate her having my back, her kindness, her sense of humor, her ethical and moral backbone, I always feel like I can trust her and that she wants the best for me. Jen is incredibly special. She is truly an amazing coach, mentor and human (I know I already said that but it had to be said again!)
